{"tid":1966421,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"盧斯達：熱血公民多一個議席，就多一個迫害他人的資源渠道。","createTime":"2020-04-10T07:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T13:38:37.000Z","uid":352349,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29dcc24e5bf757c83218a1529061bcc58a3e1370","tid":1966421,"uid":352349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"//鄭松泰本人，則是黨性大於人性。立法會裡面，沒有一個本土派的議席。他在這個議席所收到的公帑，只會成為熱血公民和「陳雲支持者」這兩個邪教幫會用來欺壓無辜者的資源。想想鄭松泰用公共資源來養幾個閒人，已經可以每日全天候開分身網絡欺凌異己、在高登不斷開帖帶風向。熱血公民想選區議會，想補選，這已經不是政治問題，而是他們多一個議席，就多一個迫害他人的資源渠道。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本土派作為反對派陣營最有活力的部份，已經受熱血公民和陳雲拖累了太久。不清除這兩個惡劣的幫會，本土派會死，反對派也將失去在野派，可以繼續怠工。在公在私，是公也是私，用他們九個月之前的話說：這是復仇的時刻，也是救自己和香港的時刻。//<br />\n<br />\n盧斯達：鄭松泰不是本土派，那會是甚麼派？<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2017/06/lewis-local/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F06%2Flewis-local%2F&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi68jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=6355abb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2017/06/lewis-local/</a>"},{"pid":"d89b4887387d8014f751eb922212e182ac9fd446","tid":1966421,"uid":76690,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"又搞分化&hellip;"},{"pid":"6260b33d50f78c04a91466b5174d8cd6cd8a8671","tid":1966421,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【國際戰線，靠你支持！】</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">頂住人民幣，對抗大外宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>為美國醫護捐贈醫療物資</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharity.gofundme.com%2Fo%2Fen%2Fcampaign%2Fmasks-empowerment-